</div><input type="button" value=181 onclick="showDiv(181)"/><div id=181  style="display:none;" ><p>DOC ID : 181 with score = 1.116572792116522</p>
<DOCNO> LA010189-0073 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 181 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
January 1, 1989, Sunday, Bulldog Edition 
